articles.author: Ivan Mehta
articles.title: Pixel 10 Pro Fold review: Google’s bet to make foldables sturdy - TechCrunch
articles.description: Google’s Pixel 10 Pro Fold improves durability with a tighter hinge, IP68 rating, a bigger battery, and brighter display, but its weaker camera system compared to the Pixel 10 Pro muddies its “Pro” branding.
articles.content: The Pixel 10 Pro Fold won’t look very different if you place it next to last year’s Pixel 9 Pro Fold. Besides Google’s AI chops, there is not much of an overhaul at first glance. However, this is the… [+5633 chars]
